== 製作 ==
電影的劇本由{{Link-en|羅伯特·D·西格爾|Robert D. Siegel}}撰寫，改编自雷·克罗克的自传和一部未经授权的传记<ref>{{Cite news |first=Robert |last=Seigel |date=2017-01-25 |title='The Founder' Follows Salesman's Genius Idea To Franchise McDonald's |work=All Things Considered |publisher=NPR |url=http://www.npr.org/2017/01/25/511655874/the-founder-follows-salesmans-genius-idea-to-franchise-mcdonalds |accessdate=2017-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170130135546/http://www.npr.org/2017/01/25/511655874/the-founder-follows-salesmans-genius-idea-to-franchise-mcdonalds |archive-date=2017-01-30 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。据早期的报道，影片的创作模式与《[[血色将至|血色将至]]》和《[[社交网络_(电影)|社交网络]]》一脉相承。[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]将本片列入2014年最佳未制作剧本的第13位<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.thewrap.com/weinstein-company-wins-bidding-war-for-michael-keatons-mcdonalds-movie-the-founder-exclusive/|title=Weinstein Company Wins Bidding War for Michael Keaton's McDonald's Movie 'The Founder' (Exclusive)|publisher=TheWrap|date=2015-03-02|accessdate=2015-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150303013609/http://www.thewrap.com/weinstein-company-wins-bidding-war-for-michael-keatons-mcdonalds-movie-the-founder-exclusive/|archive-date=2015-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2014/12/black-list-2014-announcement-schedule-1201324672/|title=Black List 2014 Gets Star Treatment In 10th Anniversary Announcement Monday|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2014-12-14|accessdate=2015-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150409010938/http://deadline.com/2014/12/black-list-2014-announcement-schedule-1201324672/|archive-date=2015-04-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年12月，[[約翰·李·漢考克|約翰·李·漢考克]]簽約執導影片<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/391277-john-lee-hancock-plans-mcdonalds-history-feature-the-founder|title=John Lee Hancock Plans McDonald's History Story, The Founder|publisher={{Link-en|ComingSoon.net|CraveOnline}}|date=2014-12-10|accessdate=2015-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/2015040211412