== 發行 ==
2015年3月2日，[[韦恩斯坦公司|韦恩斯坦公司]]出资700美元买下影片发行权<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.variety.com/2015/film/news/weinstein-co-buys-michael-keatons-mcdonalds-movie-the-founder-1201443179/|title=Weinstein Co. Buys Michael Keaton's McDonald's Movie 'The Founder'|work=Variety|date=2015-03-02|accessdate=2015-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150302123423/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/weinstein-co-buys-michael-keatons-mcdonalds-movie-the-founder-1201443179/|archive-date=2015-03-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年3月26日，片厂宣布影片上映日期为2016年11月25日<ref>{{Cite news|last1=D'Alessandro|first1=Anthony|title=Michael Keaton Starrer 'The Founder' Gets Release Date; Focus World Rounds Out 2015 Slate|url=http://www.deadline.com/2015/03/michael-keaton-founder-a-little-chaos-kate-winslet-cop-car-kevin-bacon-1201399587/|accessdate=2015-04-06|publisher=Deadline.com|date=2015-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402192521/http://deadline.com/2015/03/michael-keaton-founder-a-little-chaos-kate-winslet-cop-car-kevin-bacon-1201399587/|archive-date=2015-04-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年3月，影片移档到2016年8月5日<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/the-founder-lion-release-date-change-weinstein-co-1201712527/|title=Weinstein Co.’s ‘The Founder’ Moves To August; ‘Lion’ To Roar During Thanksgiving Week|publisher=Deadline.com|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2016-03-01|accessdate=2016-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160302095300/http://deadline.com/2016/03/the-founder-lion-release-date-change-weinstein-co-1201712527/|archive-date=2016-03-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年7月13日，上映日期再度拖延到2016年12月16日，公映日期为之后的2017年1月20日<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2016/07/13/founder-release-date-michael-keaton-mcdonalds|title=Michael Keaton's McDonald's movie The Founder gets awards season release date|publisher=Entertainment Weekly|first=Devan|last=Coggan|date=2016-07-13|accessdate=2016-07-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160714181524/http://www.ew.com/article/2016/07/13/founder-release-date-michael-keaton-mcdonalds|archive-date=2016-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。为了入选[[第89届奥斯卡金像奖|2016年奥斯卡]]，影片最终于2016年12月7日在美国{{Le|聚光灯好莱坞剧院|ArcLight Hollywood}}首映<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/12/the-founder-michael-keaton-mcdonalds-1201865619/|title=Weinstein Co.’s McDonald’s Movie ‘The Founder’ Will Open Doors Early|website=Deadline.com|first=Anthony|last=D'Alessandro|date=2016-12-06|accessdate=2016-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208130302/http://deadline.com/2016/12/the-founder-michael-keaton-mcdonalds-1201865619/|archive-date=2016-12-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>，次年1月20日公映。

2017年2月，影片制作公司{{Le|FilmNation Entertainment|FilmNation Entertainment}}起诉韦恩斯坦公司，索偿1500万美元。韦恩斯坦公司于2017年1月27日，即影片上映一周后发行《[[金爆內幕|金爆內幕]]》。FilmNation声称此举违反合约，两家公司已经达成协议，韦恩公司不会在影片上映一周前或一周后发行电影<ref name=lawsuit/><ref name=lawsuit2/>。

== 評價 ==
=== 票房 ===
影片北美票房1280万美元，海外票房1030万美元，全球票房总计2310万美元<ref name="BOM">{{Cite web |url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt4276820/?ref_=bo_se_r_1 |title=The Founder (2016) |website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |access-date=October 12, 2017 |archive-date=2022-02-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220207114600/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/title/tt4276820/?ref_=bo_se_r_1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。影片在北美与《[[分裂_(电影)|分裂]]》、《{{Le|盖文·斯通的复活|The Resurrection of Gavin Stone}}》和《[[极限特工：终极回归|极限特工：终极回归]]》同日上映，广泛发行连同《[[二十世纪女性|二十世纪女性]]》。上映首周末原计划从1115家影院中收获约300万美元票房<ref name="preview">{{Cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/01/split-xxx-return-of-xander-cage-the-founder-box-office-preview-1201888052/ |title=‘Split’ And ‘xXx’ Merge Into Market While ‘The Founder’ May Get Lost In Heavy Traffic – Box Office Preview |work=Deadline.com |access-date=2017-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803141311/http://deadline.com/2017/01/split-xxx-return-of-xander-cage-the-founder-box-office-preview-1201888052/ |archive-date=2017-08-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但最终只收获380万美元，在票房榜上位列第9<ref name="opening">{{Cite web|title=Uni/Blumhouse’s ‘Split’ Is A Hit With High $39M To $40M+; ‘Xander Cage’ Falls Down|url=http://deadline.com/2017/01/split-xxx-return-of-xander-cage-the-founder-late-night-thursday-previews-box-office-1201889940/|access-date=2017-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803140008/http://deadline.com/2017/01/split-xxx-return-of-xander-cage-the-founder-late-night-thursday-previews-box-office-1201889940/|archive-date=2017-08-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。影片第二周收获260万美元票房，同比下降23.4%<ref name="second">{{Cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2017/01/dogs-purpose-split-resident-evil-gold-box-office-1201895463/ |title=Is Controversy Impacting ‘A Dog’s Purpose’ At The Box Office? |work=Deadline.com |access-date=2017-08-03 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/query?url=http%3A%2F%2Fdeadline.com%2F2017%2F01%2Fdogs-purpose-split-resident-evil-gold-box-office-1201895463%2F&date=2018-06-23 |archive-date=2018-06-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

