[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度81%，基於收集的235篇評論，平均分為6.95/10<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_founder/|title=The Founder (2017)|website=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2017-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170116181542/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/the_founder|archive-date=2017-01-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上得到66分<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-founder |title=The Founder reviews |publisher=Metacritic |accessdate=2016-12-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161210000446/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/the-founder |archive-date=2016-12-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，收穫普遍好評。

